## 1. Project Description

**Finance Buddy** is an AI-first personal finance companion that teaches young adults how to manage money — from budgeting and saving to investing and credit building. Users name their AI buddy, complete a personalized onboarding quiz, and receive a tailored financial education experience powered by the Anthropic Claude API.

The app unifies six tools that young adults currently need *six separate apps* for: budgeting (Mint/YNAB), paper trading (Investopedia Simulator), AI Q&A (ChatGPT), credit education (Credit Karma), loan management (no good option exists), and fraud protection (no consumer-grade option exists). Finance Buddy replaces all six with a single companion that knows the user's full financial picture.

Finance Buddy is **not a trading platform** and **not a robo-advisor**. It is a **financial education engine wrapped in a companion experience** — where AI is the product, not a feature.

