The **Total Addressable Market** for personal finance apps targeting the 16–25 demographic in North America is approximately **$2.1 billion annually** (Grand View Research, 2024 — personal finance software market, youth segment). Even capturing **0.05% of the addressable market** — 21,000 paying users at an average $10/month — represents $2.5M ARR, a realistic target for a venture-backed seed round.

**Year 1 projection** (assuming 10,000 registered users after 6 months of marketing, representing ~0.02% of the 45M target demographic):
